845
00:50:30,193 --> 00:50:31,611
No, not that. [chuckles]

846
00:50:32,237 --> 00:50:34,364
Babe. [stammers, sighs]

847
00:50:34,448 --> 00:50:36,324
Whatever, just forget it. [chuckles]

848
00:50:36,408 --> 00:50:37,909
Babe, let's go!

849
00:50:37,993 --> 00:50:39,661
