850
00:50:44,708 --> 00:50:47,586
- [squeals, chuckling]
- [chuckling]

851
00:50:50,922 --> 00:50:52,340
Let's go, babe!

852
00:50:53,633 --> 00:50:55,218
Come on, babe!

853
00:50:56,386 --> 00:50:58,555
[both chuckle]

854
00:51:13,695 --> 00:51:14,821
[camera shutters]

855
00:51:49,272 --> 00:51:50,690
- Ooh.
- [Ji-hyeok] Ta-da!

856
00:51:50,774 --> 00:51:52,067
