857
00:51:52,651 --> 00:51:54,319
- Me?
- [camera shutters]

858
00:51:54,986 --> 00:51:56,112
[gasps]

859
00:52:01,243 --> 00:52:02,327
Mmm.

860
00:52:04,871 --> 00:52:05,872
Hmm?

861
00:52:12,546 --> 00:52:14,297
[chuckles]

862
