- [speaks indistinctly]
- Mmm.

869
00:52:41,867 --> 00:52:44,160
- Hold on. You have something here.
- Mmm?

870
00:52:44,244 --> 00:52:45,245
Huh?

871
00:52:45,745 --> 00:52:46,746
No, not there.

872
00:52:47,414 --> 00:52:48,498
[song continues]

873
00:53:20,780 --> 00:53:21,781
