a new market for us.

902
00:54:39,901 --> 00:54:40,944
- Mm-hmm.
- [Go-eun] Hmm.

903
00:54:41,027 --> 00:54:43,863
- That's true.
- If I could offer a tip,

904
00:54:43,947 --> 00:54:45,907
I'd say start recording everything
