where it went wrong.

911
00:54:57,961 --> 00:55:00,130
Oh, that makes sense.

912
00:55:00,213 --> 00:55:01,381
Thank you.

913
00:55:01,464 --> 00:55:02,632
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

914
