I'm not sure how it should be tied.

928
00:56:32,931 --> 00:56:34,182
The way you tie it?

929
00:56:37,977 --> 00:56:39,062
[chuckles]

930
00:56:46,444 --> 00:56:47,862
[speaks indistinctly]

931
00:56:47,946 --> 00:56:49,364
[chuckles]

932
00:56:49,447 --> 00:56:51,282
[chuckles, speaks indistinctly]

933
00:56:51,366 --> 00:56:52,700
