953
00:57:58,683 --> 00:57:59,809
WITH BABY

954
00:58:01,311 --> 00:58:02,770
- Ta-da!
- Ta-da!

955
00:58:02,854 --> 00:58:04,522
- [all cheering]
- [Gyeong-min] Okay!

956
00:58:06,733 --> 00:58:09,360
- This is excellent!
- We did it!

957
00:58:09,444 --> 00:58:11,029
- [Gyeong-min] We did it!
- Baby carrier.

958
00:58:11,613 --> 00:58:14,491
