1016
01:00:47,477 --> 01:00:49,687
This will be out on the market
next week, right?

1017
01:00:49,771 --> 01:00:50,813
I'm not dreaming, am I?

1018
01:00:50,897 --> 01:00:52,982
[squealing]

1019
01:00:53,066 --> 01:00:54,233
