1025
01:01:04,369 --> 01:01:06,663
- This came out so nicely.
- Look at it.

1026
01:01:10,458 --> 01:01:12,669
[Da-rim] This is
the same as our prototype.

1027
01:01:12,752 --> 01:01:15,129
